headline: Nvidia Says All Customers Will Be ‘Priority’ Despite OpenAI Deal
summary: “Our investments will not change our focus or impact supply to our other customers,” Nvidia said in a statement late Monday.  “We will continue to make every customer a top priority, with or without any equity stake.”  Earlier on Monday, Nvidia and OpenAI announced that they’d signed a letter of intent to pursue the $100 billion deal.
